            "type": "paragraph"
          },
          {
            "content": [
              {
                "text": "- post a structured PR comment that the Junior workflow watches for, OR",
                "type": "text"
              },
              {
                "type": "hardBreak"
              },
              {
                "text": "- set a label on the PR that re-triggers the Junior workflow.",
                "type": "text"
              }
            ],
            "type": "paragraph"
          },
          {
            "content": [
              {
                "text": "Pick one and document. Make sure the loop has a hard cap so it cannot run indefinitely.",
                "type": "text"
